    rdfs:label "NetworkTrafficCommunityDeviation" ;
    d3f:d3fend-id "D3-NTCD" ;
    d3f:kb-article "## How it works Hosts/users within a computer network are analyzed to identify communities of hosts which frequently communicate. Future communications between communities that don't usually communicate can then be detected. For example, if a community of hosts that communicate in support of a comp" ;
