d3f:SenderMTAReputationAnalysis a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "SenderMTAReputationAnalysis" ;
    d3f:d3fend-id "D3-SMRA" ;
    d3f:kb-article "## How it works The sender message transfer agent (MTA) trust rating can be considered an indicator of the level of security risk and/or a trust level associated with sender MTAs in an email header. The features considered in determining the trust rating may include: * Length of time MTA has inter" ;
    d3f:owl_named_individual "true" ;
