    d3f:d3fend-id "D3-SBV" ;
    d3f:kb-article "## How it works System service applications may originate from the operating system installation or third-party applications installed with administrative privileges. These services have an entry point of some executable file-- a binary or a script. Attackers sometimes modify these executables to la" ;
