    d3f:d3fend-id "D3-SCA" ;
    d3f:kb-article "## How it works System calls are APIs between a user application and the operating system [1]. By analyzing a process's use of these APIs, it is, in some cases, possible to ascertain whether a program is exhibiting unauthorized behavior, including trying to escalate its privileges. ### Gathering" ;
